s)<br />(<span class="script-hebrew" style="font-size: 115%;" dir="rtl">טָהֳרוֹת</span>&#8206;)</td></tr><tr style="vertical-align:top;"><td class="navbox-list" style="padding:0px;text-align:center; padding:3px;;;background:#C0FFC0;;width:10em;"><div>
