<li id="cite_note-20"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-20">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">The plural term (singular <b>tanna</b>) for the <a href="/wiki/Rabbi" title="Rabbi">Rabbinic</a> sages whose views are recorded in the Mishnah; from the Aramaic root <i>tanna</i> (תנא) equivalent for the Hebrew root <i>shanah</i> (שנה), as in <i>Mishnah</i>.</span>
