<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Historical_study">Historical study</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Mishnah&amp;action=edit&amp;section=22" title="Edit section: Historical study"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
<ul><li>Shalom Carmy (Ed.) <i>Modern Scholarship in the Study of Torah: Contributions and Limitations</i> Jason Aronson, Inc.</li>
